          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "天下有道，知足知止，無求於外，各修其內而已，故卻走馬以治田糞也。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 11
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "貪欲無厭，不修其內，各求於外，故戎馬生於郊也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
